Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H282795&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke, who was killed by the \Ngreat organization GOD along with his father...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...revived as Kamen Rider X, thanks to his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Keisuke's lover, Ryouko, side with GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is Kiriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who fights against the mysterious GOD, Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD, the Shadow of Fear!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you call for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Medusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come to test your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shall feast on life blood as a sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Once human blood is absorbed into my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My body will be able to exert \Nmany times more power than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk, turn into stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Medusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you our command later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Medusa, I'm telling you our command.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job is to find out how \NProfessor Kogure developed Alpha Gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the terrifying poison of Alpha Gas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...every single human in Japan shall die in madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, first...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...kidnap the professor's only daughter, Saeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the daughter, Kogure Saeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogure Saeko. Kogure Saeko. \NYour companion is waiting at the back gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange. No one other than us three came with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going. Please wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Kogure Saeko, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be held captive for Professor Kogure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me! Hepl me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Jin Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you off the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you targeted by GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They were going to hold me captive for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to sound rude, but who's your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Kogure Seijiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That doctor of science?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke. You interfered again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't run away from me, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke, that jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Ryouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I don't know where Keisuke is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell into my trap, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD must be behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomi, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The professor was... Some strange guys came in...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...and took the professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But, where did they take him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was punched...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...and then I went unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it... I knew it, my father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the amusement park...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...and now, the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's GOD's target this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father should come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,These are orders from the GOD General Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider X, Jin Keisuke, kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do so by any means possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill that detestable X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura. Untie me and get me out of here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Miura! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor. If you tell me where the blueprints for the Alpha Gas are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...then I'll untie you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're a member of them as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you've finally realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know my true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My true identity is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The assassin of GOD, Medusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Kogure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you adore your daughter, then confess already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you want your daughter Saeko alive or dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...is up for you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll let you think for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I need to do until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my sight, obstacles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It came from the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Saeko, stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Saeko... this is your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill Jin Keisuke for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you say, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Saeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! It's me, Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A snake! A snake is going to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you were hypnotized.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Saeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, X!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Medusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad for you that I wasn't the professor's assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pierce through fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The time bomb's switch has been set, \Nso that when X Rider comes to rescue you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...it will make a hot explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Medusa. X Rider has attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need this house if it's in exchange for X Rider's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll make it explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this child?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's bait in order to lock up X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to be locked up with X Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll set this onto the ceiling and we'll blow them up along with X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to achieve their method, they won't choose their targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the rule of GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Saeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Saeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He was lured by a fake voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Saeko, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you be sacrificed for X Rider's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had commands from the \NGeneral Commander to kill X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But, he won't tell me to kill the child as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave! She's important bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'll let the child go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an ally of GOD! \NActing so selfishly is unforgiveable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can get X Rider without the child!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The time bomb has been set and the underground corridor has been opened to let X Rider through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He will soon come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Saeko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Ryouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Saeko, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eliminate all traitors of GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I, X Rider, will save you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A time bomb has been set!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use. It'll take much more than my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This wall is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This mark is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a hidden door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Saeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Saeko, Professor, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fell into my trap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Medusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Great Rotation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:21:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,See this, Medusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider X, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall turn into stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You doged it! I don't have any more energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X, who is sent to fight against GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That desolate fight has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have time to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it, Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(45,0)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"The One-Eyed Monster's Kidnapping Operation!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.59,0:24:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.59,0:24:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.18,0:24:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.18,0:24:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider